WEBVTT

00:00:00.439 --> 00:00:04.064
Good morning, family! How are y'all doing? I'm excited to be here today.

00:00:04.065 --> 00:00:17.034
I have some things on my heart that the Lord has been talking to me about in prayer: interceding for Israel and for Iran, and what's going on in the Middle East right now.

00:00:17.035 --> 00:00:27.971
There is an escalation of things, and I'm getting some very heavy warnings whenever I pray.

00:00:27.972 --> 00:00:38.502
One of the things I was feeling a caution about talking about was this thing going down in Cuba.

00:00:38.502 --> 00:00:45.199
I tried to tell you all in the prayer video I did that the Lord showed me some things.

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:59.081
I saw some meetings, some secret things taking place, and the Lord said, 'Go back to the 1960s.'During that timeframe, when Kennedy was president and what was going on there.

00:00:59.082 --> 00:01:09.470
I wasn't going to reveal a lot of what I saw because of safety for my family, but I will tell you this: it's something to pray about.

00:01:09.471 --> 00:01:21.294
This is very serious what the Lord showed me and what they were planning—old ties were being reunited.

00:01:21.295 --> 00:01:36.136
It was brought up in the Russian news a couple of days ago, talking about the exact same thing the Lord warned me about in prayer weeks prior.

00:01:36.137 --> 00:01:44.655
So here we are, another major thing for people to pray about: Havana. I'll leave that there.

00:01:44.656 --> 00:02:02.481
Now I want to go to the things the Lord has been warning me about: praying about Israel striking Iran and this causing a major uprising in the Middle East.

00:02:02.483 --> 00:02:08.043
The United States will be coinciding with this; it will be about the oil.

00:02:08.044 --> 00:02:18.026
As I said, the Lord showed me oil prices skyrocketing in the Middle East, the petrodollar, and things like that controlling the economy.

00:02:18.027 --> 00:02:33.699
There's a lot of manipulation and darkness with this. As a prophetic intercessor, the Lord shows me things, and I have to check about saying this or that.

00:02:33.700 --> 00:02:42.615
He has not released me to say everything, but I'm going to tell you we need to pray over strikes against Iran.

00:02:42.616 --> 00:02:54.579
It's going to increase. It's about the oil, the green agenda, and all the world economic stuff.

00:02:54.580 --> 00:02:58.053
After they had that meeting, I'm telling you, more stuff is coming.

00:02:58.054 --> 00:03:03.862
I'm trying to warn you about what I'm seeing and praying about in the spirit so you can pray with me.

00:03:03.863 --> 00:03:11.598
This is not a 'Debbie Downer'or 'doom and gloom'message; I'm trying to warn you as a watchman to pray and intercede.

00:03:11.599 --> 00:03:24.816
We have power and authority in the spirit realm. As far as Cuba goes, I'm still praying in the spirit over it.

00:03:24.817 --> 00:03:36.693
I haven't received a direction of danger per se; it's just like I get these pulses like heartbeats.

00:03:36.694 --> 00:03:55.958
The Lord will warn me about these heartbeats, and it's like he says, 'I need you to intercede for this.'The more I pray, the more he shows me pieces and meetings.

00:03:55.959 --> 00:04:12.711
It's a caution—that's a good way to say it. Do you remember those games at the arcades where that mole keeps sticking his head up and you keep hitting him? Hit that mole in the head, smack him down, and he falls.

00:04:12.712 --> 00:04:23.702
That is the devil; he is always trying to rear his head, and we take our spiritual sword and smack him in the head with that Whac-A-Mole action and keep hitting him down in there.

00:04:23.703 --> 00:04:39.596
He tries to figure out where to stick his head up next, but we're going to keep hitting him as fast as we can to keep that devil down.

00:04:39.597 --> 00:04:53.242
He tries to stir up drama in the earth, like everything down in Eagle Pass and at the border. He keeps trying to rear his head.

00:04:53.243 --> 00:05:05.288
We have to get to the point where we're not just putting the devil's fires out after he starts them; we keep the fires from starting.

00:05:05.289 --> 00:05:13.643
We stop chasing the devil; we are ahead because we know what's coming.

00:05:13.644 --> 00:05:19.274
It's time to go deeper and come up higher in intercessory prayer.

00:05:19.275 --> 00:05:26.508
The Holy Spirit will show you things to come and show you how to stop them before they even start.

00:05:26.509 --> 00:05:31.610
He’ll show you where that 'whack-a-mole'head is going to come up before it even happens.

00:05:31.611 --> 00:05:40.590
He'll say, 'It's going to come up over there next,'and you hit it before he even has a chance to stick his head out of that hole.

00:05:40.591 --> 00:05:58.622
I'm trying to give you a visual so the Body of Christ understands it's time to come up higher in prayer and the authority we have through Jesus Christ.

00:05:58.623 --> 00:06:06.333
We are seated with him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities, powers, and might.

00:06:06.334 --> 00:06:18.661
The Holy Spirit dwells inside of you, and we are able to take authority and dominion over the devil. We shouldn't be going around just putting out fires.

00:06:18.662 --> 00:06:34.767
Now, my wife is going to read this prophetic warning about Israel and Iran that was given several years ago.

00:06:34.768 --> 00:06:40.262
I hope this blesses you. Keep watching, and I'll be back in a little bit to close this out.

00:06:40.263 --> 00:06:49.185
We'll pray over Iran, Israel, and the peace of Jerusalem. I'm not trying to preach fear; I'm trying to wake you all up.

00:06:49.186 --> 00:06:58.141
We are in the last of the last days. Jesus is coming soon. Look at the economy and the signs in the heavens.

00:06:58.142 --> 00:07:13.191
God is trying to tell the people, 'I'm coming.'I hope you're ready. (Wife): This is a prophetic word from November 28th, 2019.

00:07:13.192 --> 00:07:20.114
I was observing a meeting of military leaders with the supreme leader of the Iran regime.

00:07:20.115 --> 00:07:28.985
They were seated at a very large conference table, curved like an oval.

00:07:28.986 --> 00:07:38.084
On the far end was the head man who had a white beard and was wearing a white head wrap and a long dark brown robe.

00:07:38.085 --> 00:07:47.430
Flanking him on both sides were men in military uniforms. They were speaking in their language, but somehow I understood the conversation.

00:07:47.431 --> 00:07:55.009
In a nutshell, the leader said that Iran is in a crisis both from without and within.

00:07:55.010 --> 00:08:02.534
Within, he said it was the rise of Christian revival in Iran. From without, it is economic.

00:08:02.535 --> 00:08:09.383
'The Great Satan,'as he called the United States, has nearly crippled our economy.

00:08:09.384 --> 00:08:31.758
Then he said Allah had spoken to him to gather those in that room and tell them the time has now come to go to war to end all wars, to destroy the 'Little Satan'and mortally wound the 'Great Satan.'I realized this referred to Israel and the U.S.

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:48.712
Everyone at the table then applauded and shouted in unison, 'Our God is greater!'and 'Death to our eternal enemies!'The leader continued and said the Mahdi Messiah is about to appear, and we are to prepare his way.

00:08:48.713 --> 00:09:00.426
Even if Iran falls, we must destroy the Zionist regime. All is now prepared; we have the weapons to overwhelm them and wipe the Little Satan out and liberate the Middle East.

00:09:00.427 --> 00:09:07.795
Then they all stood and shouted over and over, 'Our God is greater!

00:09:07.796 --> 00:09:27.837
Death to the infidels!'Then the Holy Spirit said to me, 'Iran's fanatical regime has plans in place for a sudden, all-out attack on Israel.'They plan to use the element of surprise to launch a simultaneous missile attack from all sides.

00:09:27.838 --> 00:09:34.345
They believe it will overwhelm the IDF missile defenses by the sheer number of missiles.

00:09:34.346 --> 00:09:39.733
They have nuclear capability now, though it is limited and untested.

00:09:39.734 --> 00:09:48.529
Their strategy is to knock out the missile defenses first and then try to sneak in the atomic warheads in the deluge.

00:09:48.530 --> 00:09:54.673
They have ten nuclear devices hidden among their arsenal, including one submarine.

00:09:54.674 --> 00:10:00.999
Tell my prayer warriors to take authority and intercede now so this evil plot will be stopped.

00:10:01.000 --> 00:11:30.675
(Speaker): Regarding the vision I had back in November, the Antichrist agenda was trying to come on faster.

00:11:30.676 --> 00:11:53.177
They're even asking for the Mahdi. I told y'all that they worship the Mahdi on Fridays during the seven years of tribulation.

00:11:53.178 --> 00:12:01.356
I told you I believe the person I saw was MBS. Most people say there's no way, or they say it's Obama or Trump.

00:12:01.357 --> 00:12:14.386
I'm telling you, you don't know what you're talking about because I was there.

00:12:14.387 --> 00:12:21.215
I was with Jesus Christ himself walking the streets of America, and I saw it on the screen.

00:12:21.216 --> 00:12:29.786
I'm trying to warn you ahead of time. Does it change anything?

00:12:29.787 --> 00:12:35.369
No, but it's something you can pray about and have eyes to see.

00:12:35.370 --> 00:12:48.026
I could not see his eyes or his nose—the Lord blocked it out—but the mannerisms, the way he talks, and the way he flows are identical.

00:12:48.027 --> 00:12:57.247
And who is on the news over there all the time right now? Who is the main spokesperson for the people?

00:12:57.248 --> 00:13:10.270
The Prince. It isn't anybody else, and it just started to happen. I'm not going to be here to see it anyway.

00:13:10.271 --> 00:13:16.154
Jesus is coming back for his bride, and we're going to be caught up in a moment, in the twinkling of an eye.

00:13:16.155 --> 00:13:24.065
We're all going to be changed. We're going home in the Rapture.

00:13:24.066 --> 00:13:30.825
We're not appointed unto wrath. God is not a wife-beater; he is not going to beat his bride.

00:13:30.826 --> 00:13:59.527
He loves us. For me and my house, we're going in the Rapture. I want to pray for the safety of America.

00:13:59.528 --> 00:14:08.487
We have open borders from a rogue president who doesn't know what he's doing, and people are pouring over.

00:14:08.488 --> 00:20:45.299
It's not just people seeking refuge; there are terrorists. This isn't Hollywood; it's real life.

00:20:45.300 --> 00:21:24.224
I see mountains right now and hidden things in Iran—hills and caves with hidden things.

00:21:24.225 --> 00:22:44.449
The Lord said the Israeli intelligence knows about these things.

00:22:44.450 --> 00:22:57.478
I see canisters; they're like silver canisters full of liquids, some of them gas.

00:22:57.479 --> 00:25:09.439
They are like huge kegs in an underground tunnel system. I see a yellow mustard gas; it is a gas in these, these Agent Orange.

00:25:09.440 --> 00:26:25.912
It's neurological. I see a long truck, and they are trying to transport these things.

00:26:25.913 --> 00:27:59.552
I see them trying to sneak the back way through the hills. It's coming through Damascus. I call every hidden thing to be exposed in the name of Jesus.

00:27:59.553 --> 00:28:43.678
I thank you, Lord, that you're guiding the intelligence and speaking to them through signs.

00:28:43.679 --> 00:30:32.999
I just saw Iraq flash before me—the northern part. I see Jordan, going clear into Syria.

00:30:33.000 --> 00:31:24.778
I see them chanting 'Death to America.'It's a rising up of so much hatred.

00:31:24.779 --> 00:32:03.972
Lord, about that gas—it makes the victim throw up and causes convulsions.

00:32:03.973 --> 00:33:05.199
It causes huge burns and welts upon the skin. I see welts like your skin is melting.

00:33:05.200 --> 00:36:08.690
We pray for protection against this evil activity. I thank you, Lord, that no weapon formed against us would prosper.

00:36:08.691 --> 00:36:36.991
I'm going to end this video here and pray over this some more.

00:36:36.992 --> 00:36:49.880
Put a smile on your face; Jesus loves you so much. God bless you guys; have a nice day.

